        "action": "Place sanctions on the Sri Lankan Government",
        "additional_details": "This is arguably against their human rights and their freedoms of religion. Cremations are against the religion of Islam, Judaism and the like. This should be condemned and sanctions must be placed on the Sri Lankan government if they do not change their policy.",
        "background": "The Sri Lankan are requiring the cremation of the dead, meaning people are are unable to bury them as they should in accordance to their religion.",
